high_descs: Turn left, move to the table left of the plate, near the coffee maker.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Slice the tomato on the table.
Move to the table near the tomato.
Put the knife on the table.
Move to the table near the tomato.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the table.
Turn right, move to in front of the stove.
Put the tomato slice in the pot.
Pick up the pot from the stove.
Turn left, move to in front of the refrigerator.
Put the pot in the refrigerator.

Pick up a slice of tomato from its end

Put the tomato in the pot that is on the stove

Put the pot in the fridge
